---
title: Candy | Home
layout: layouts/base.njk
bodyClass: candy-page
templateEngineOverride: njk, md
contentContainerClass: container-fluid
metaDescription: Candy is an Eleventy project starter with loads of sugar on top.
---
<div class="row justify-content-end parallax-window">
  <div class="col-6 col-lg-5 pr-5">
    <h1 class="super-title">Candy</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      <span class="candy-logo">Candy</span> is an Eleventy project starter with loads of sugar on top. Sweet extras like ...<br>
      <span class="txt-rotate" data-period="1000" data-rotate='[ "Bootstrap 4.", "Gulp.", "Sass.", "Custom Widgets.", "jQuery.", "PrismJS.", "Google Fonts.", "Custom Filters.", "SEO Optimizations." ]'>Bootstrap 4, Gulp, Sass, PrismJS, and more!</span>
      <span class="txt-rotate-space">&nbsp;</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row deploy-netlify-row p-3 justify-content-center fluid-row">
  <div class="col-12 col-md-7 col-lg-6">
    <div>Get your own clone of Eleventy + <span class="candy-logo">Candy</span> deployed to <a href="https://www.netlify.com">Netlify</a>! Click the <i>Deploy to Netlify</i> button and follow the instructions.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 col-md-5 col-lg-3">
    <p><a href="https://app.netlify.com/start/deploy?repository=https://github.com/stickhandle/eleventy-candy"><img class="netlify-button" src="https://www.netlify.com/img/deploy/button.svg" alt="Deploy to Netlify"></a></p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container mt-3">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="card-deck">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header center">
          <h4 class="card-title">üç´ Delicious Build Pipeline</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-text">
            <table>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Yarn&nbsp;<i class="fab fa-yarn"></i> for dependencies.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Gulp&nbsp;<i class="fab fa-gulp"></i> build pipeline with pre-processing of images, CSS, JS.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Nunjucks templates.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Markdown-it&nbsp;<i class="fab fa-markdown"></i> for content + footnote and emoji support.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">11ty pulls it all together.</td></tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header center">
          <h4 class="card-title">üç¨ Yummy Display Goodies</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-text">
            <table>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text"><i class="fab fa-sass" style="font-size: 24px"></i> for sassy CSS preprocessing.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Bootstrap responsive component library baked in.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">jQuery ready.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">PrismJS for syntax highlighting.</td></tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header center">
          <h4 class="card-title">üç≠ Candy Custom Treats</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-text">
            <table>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Blog and Portfolio ready.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Custom Related Posts, Favorites and Tag List widgets.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Custom tags page.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Custom filters.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">Ready for RSS.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="card-bullet"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></td><td class="card-bullet-text">SEO Optimizations.</td></tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>  
<div class="row fluid-row">
  <div class="col">
    <blockquote cite="Charles Schulz">All I really need is love, but a little candy now and then doesn't hurt!</blockquote>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col"><h3>From the Blog ...</h3></div>
  </div>
  {%- set cls = cycler("odd", "even") -%}
  {%- for post in collections.posts.slice(0, 3) %}
    <div class="blog-list-item h3-to-mini {{ cls.next() }}">
        <div class="row">
            {% if post.data.mainImageFilename -%}
                {% if cls.current == 'odd' -%}
                    {% include "blog-item-odd.njk" -%}
                {% else -%}
                    {% include "blog-item-even.njk" -%}
                {% endif -%}
            {% else -%}
                {% include "blog-item-noimage.njk" -%}
            {% endif -%}
        </div>
    </div>
  {%- endfor %}
</div>
<div class="row fluid-row">
  <div class="col">
    <blockquote class="bq-dark" cite="Scott Adams">You don't argue with a four-year old about why he shouldn't eat candy for dinner.</blockquote>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col"><h3>Latest from the Portfolio ...</h3></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    {%- set cls = cycler("cycle-item-a", "cycle-item-b", "cycle-item-b", "cycle-item-a") -%}
    {%- for photo in collections.sotohp.slice(0, 4) %}
        <div class="col-6 col-lg-3 h3-to-mini {{ cls.next() }}">
          {% include "photo-item.njk" -%}
        </div>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</div>





